<paragraph id="1B4254F316E32D2F0048574B410F6A2B" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">
<taxonomicName id="F0E93113CDB6E15C7FBEC57D5E0EE01D" authority="L'Herit." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Geranium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="628" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lividum">
Geranium 
<normalizedToken id="1F76CE81D4FCB9FB37C9534B676E5B53" originalValue="lívidum" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">lividum</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D7033A4C5E987240D6C5B105A231DBD4" originalValue="L’Hérit" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">L'Herit</normalizedToken>
.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="AFFB149D90EAA08DB404E4B20901AE42" pageId="null" pageNumber="628" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="42AD07CC6F2C831A25291CD7B8C68523" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Violetter Storchschnabel</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="F110B8FA0BE7F0C42A9AA3A10E8A45F8" pageId="null" pageNumber="628" type="description">
<paragraph id="6E536596F23B555CCF53BA0934FD726C" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="9B3AAB6ECFEE94C117ABD0AD91440E36" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Geranium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="628" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="phaeum">
<emphasis id="81584B2EEF88EC9A81CACA5C17DFA27C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">G. phaeum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 18) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<normalizedToken id="92A50F69FEEE7088E9E0B29913C287C6" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
nie mit braunem Fleck; 
<normalizedToken id="D610649FF43189111B6F98A35303EFDC" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
vorn 
<normalizedToken id="54F698CB9F9BF1AD781D0DACFDAA4113" originalValue="unregelmäßig" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">unregelmaessig</normalizedToken>
ausgerandet oder 
<normalizedToken id="F0AE2B6B9F230EAFE3F21B56948D34E7" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="C2911123F4CC17F795F265B1B741D3F5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">
hellviolett oder rosa; 
<normalizedToken id="4C24505576A681A0837692385989D999" originalValue="Staubfäden" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Staubfaeden</normalizedToken>
gegen den Grund 
<normalizedToken id="0856E653AC6C4018DBB9FB9901CF41D1" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
verbreitert und dort 
<normalizedToken id="61F8771773F80162706E30368392C42F" originalValue="höchstens" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">hoechstens</normalizedToken>
3mal so breit wie in der Mitte;
</emphasis>
Frucht 2,5-3 cm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="AED2E390F307395DF76BB7C169CFC6F1" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="920F84F7F204EB5AC8A72255EED2E586" originalValue="Früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="13DD75CBB8E16F621B2771DEEFFB7E27" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">
<emphasis id="CF6A0345EC220DEACA8F84D4C557DA3B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen. Vielleicht beziehen sich einzelne Angaben von 
<taxonomicName id="D3B71C84B5AA30D65E73478546286DB0" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Geranium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="628" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="phaeum">
<emphasis id="36D656B6B9F4151563A8176C8CB55990" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">G. phaeum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
hierher.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E690E7F5F7BE5C312724F2653CF7D65E" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">
<emphasis id="F491CCABB55399998933C1B12B076B1D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin, seltener montan und kollin. Feuchte, stickstoffreiche 
<normalizedToken id="778825AB0BFEFB81EF0C4F173F5ADE03" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Fettwiesen, Hochstaudenfluren, 
<normalizedToken id="1DE6BF5677507B9D5011389C60369C37" originalValue="Waldränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Waldraender</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BA239C7B0B3F9828FB4A859AF8EAEE22" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">
<emphasis id="63B751C4994D71D3F8D2563770A6AE28" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Verbreitung</emphasis>
(nicht sicher bekannt): 
<emphasis id="432FF8E31A444FAFDA5A847484195FE4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">Alpenpflanze</emphasis>
(?). - Im Gebiet: Alpen (in den Nordalpen 
<normalizedToken id="C30384D02723F62864FAF46DFE217624" originalValue="östlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">oestlich</normalizedToken>
des Brienzersees und im Tessin nicht vorhanden); nicht 
<normalizedToken id="AA224ACA2957F293BDD8BF6FBD2F4E52" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="628">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
